# Disable Middle Mouse Button functionality, as suggested here:
# https://unix.stackexchange.com/a/277488

# Disables pasting only, not the event
# "echo -n | xsel -n -i; pkill xbindkeys; xdotool click 2; xbindkeys"

# Disables MMB completely
""
  b:2 + Release

# Left-Alt + Left-Mouse-Button acts as Right-Mouse-Button
"xte 'mouseclick 3'"
  Mod1 + b:1 + Release
